  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p data-end=\"161\" data-start=\"105\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"305\" data-start=\"163\">We're thrilled to announce that we’ll be launching a <strong data-end=\"260\" data-start=\"216\">new release path for Analytics Client JS</strong>, upgrading from <strong data-end=\"304\" data-start=\"277\">version 1.1.9 to 1.1.10</strong>.</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"371\" data-start=\"307\">This release includes important fixes for the following tickets:</p>\n\n<ul data-end=\"626\" data-start=\"373\">\n\t<li data-end=\"436\" data-start=\"373\">\n\t<p data-end=\"436\" data-start=\"375\"><a data-end=\"434\" data-start=\"375\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-27615\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\">LPD-27615</a></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li data-end=\"500\" data-start=\"437\">\n\t<p data-end=\"500\" data-start=\"439\"><a data-end=\"498\" data-start=\"439\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-36626\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\">LPD-36626</a></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li data-end=\"564\" data-start=\"501\">\n\t<p data-end=\"564\" data-start=\"503\"><a data-end=\"562\" data-start=\"503\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-39188\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\">LPD-39188</a></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li data-end=\"626\" data-start=\"565\">\n\t<p data-end=\"626\" data-start=\"567\"><a data-end=\"626\" data-start=\"567\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-55350\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\">LPD-55350</a></p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p data-end=\"688\" data-start=\"628\">🕐 <strong data-end=\"652\" data-start=\"631\">Release Schedule:</strong><br data-end=\"655\" data-start=\"652\">\nThe release will be performed at <strong data-end=\"731\" data-start=\"692\">1:00 PM PST&nbsp;</strong></p>"
      },
